Description: BCBG Girls Traveler's Rucksack Olive Nylon MSRP: $75 Product Description: BCBG Girl's Rucksack (Backpack / Book bag), olive nylon outer with indigo Inner. Buckle straps for main pocket and the 2 outer pockets are for decoration. Pocket closures are magnetic. The top zipper pocket on the main flap is shallow but functional for quick access. The large interior has an additional zipper pocket slightly larger than the outer. It also has two open slip pockets, for smaller items that will fit snugly. The interior of the bag is quite deep despite it's small appearance. The exterior has brushed brass hardware. There are small metal letters near the hangar hook that spell out BCBG and also have and additional tag reading "girls". The straps for the bag are adjustable. Seller's Notes: I love this bag, wish I was still in school or traveling. It's a great day or weekend bag, for the on-the-go-gal. Functional, versatile, light weight, durable, and water resistant. The timeless style of the outer makes this a bag that will be fashionable even after the zombie apocalypse.
